{
  "texts": [
    "In cloud systems, it becomes necessary to pass data back and forth to run the models in the cloud.",
    "Performance thus becomes dependent on internet connectivity.",
    "Model latency is a more often recognized reason to opt for localized solutions, with more controlled 66 Page 28 of 41 connection speeds, especially in weaker connectivity applications such as mobile devices or edge applications.",
    "The same applies in the course of training DL models.",
    "DL models use large amounts of data in their training and the need to constantly transfer data to and from platforms creates latencies in the process."
  ]
}